    	const size_t file_size = ftell(my_file);

…I know, to be pedantic *`fseek(file,  0,  SEEK_END)` has undefined behavior for a binary stream* [[1][1]] – but frankly on the platforms where this is a problem I also don&#39;t have `fstat()` and anyway this is a topic for another question…

